modules.description: This module removes diacritics from Latin letters in UTF8 strings, converting characters like "é" to "e", and handles malformed or non-ASCII input with customizable replacements. It operates directly on UTF8-encoded strings and Unicode characters (`Uchar.t`), offering functions to simplify text for searching and comparison without altering the original UTF8 storage. Specific utilities include converting ISO 8859-1 and Windows-1252 strings to UTF8, and identifying whitespace characters.
